headline: Prudential Launches OneLeave™ to Help Simplify and Improve the Workplace Leave Experience
summary: NEWARK, N.J., February 19, 2025--Prudential Financial, Inc. (NYSE: PRU) today launched OneLeave, adding new absence and disability capabilities to help address the challenges of workplace leaves and the disruption it can create for both employers and employees.
